        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 2. External morphology and ossicles of Holothuria (Holothuria) tubulosa (s.s.) (CMNI 2021–0195). A. Dorsal surface. B. Ventral surface. Ca. Tables of dorsal and ventral surfaces (SEM). Cb. Buttons of dorsal and ventral surfaces (SEM). Da. Enlarged plates of pedicels (one enlarged plate left with SEM and the 3 other in right with LM). Db. Elongated plate of pedicels (SEM). Ea. Straight rods of tentacles (LM). Eb. Slightly arched rods of tentacles (LM)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4897624/files/figure.png" .

